                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9861" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0262</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">983 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“链”接低碳未来：协鑫集团如何重塑供应链减碳新范式？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Chaining to a low-carbon future: How GCL Group reshapes a new paradigm of supply chain carbon reduction?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郭玲玲，项明庆，何沛东，邓智</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">协鑫（集团）控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">碳足迹管理；区块链技术；供应链减碳；全生命周期理论；光伏产业；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Carbon footprint management; Blockchain technology; Supply chain carbon reduction; Life cycle theory; Photovoltaic industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着欧盟碳关税（CBAM）等国际绿色贸易壁垒加速落地，以及中国“双碳”目标下碳足迹管理体系建设的政策驱动，企业亟需应对全球碳治理规则的挑战。本案例以协鑫集团为研究对象，阐述其联合蚂蚁集团构建全球首条光伏碳链的实践，通过区块链技术实现光伏组件全生命周期碳足迹的动态追溯与透明化管理。案例重点剖析协鑫如何借助碳链建设，突破光伏组件从“摇篮”到“大门”环节的数据孤岛和信任危机，打造全链条的碳数据溯源可信链，进而赋能供应链减碳实现生态协同治理。通过本案例的学习，学生可深入理解区块链技术在供应链减碳中的核心逻辑，掌握全生命周期理论在碳足迹核算与管理中的应用，并思考企业如何通过技术创新与生态协同应对国际绿色贸易规则挑战，为行业低碳转型提供技术路径与管理经验参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the accelerated implementation of international green trade barriers such as the European Union’s carbon tariff (CBAM) and the policy-driven construction of a carbon footprint management system under China&#39;s “dual-carbon” goal, enterprises need to urgently address the challenges of global carbon governance rules. Taking GCL Group as the research object, this case describes its practice of constructing the world’s first photovoltaic carbon chain in cooperation with Ant Group, which realizes the dynamic traceability and transparent management of the carbon footprint of photovoltaic modules in their whole life cycle through blockchain technology. The case focuses on analyzing how GCL breaks through the data silos and trust crisis of photovoltaic modules from the “cradle” to the “gate” with the help of carbon chain construction, creating a credible chain of carbon data traceability for the whole chain, and thereby empowering the supply chain to reduce carbon emissions and achieve ecological collaborative governance. Through the study of this case, students can deeply understand the core logic of blockchain technology in supply chain carbon reduction, master the application of the whole life cycle theory in carbon footprint accounting and management, and think about how enterprises can respond to the challenges of international green trade rules through technological innovation and ecological synergies, so as to provide technical paths and management experience references for the industry’s low-carbon transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">碳足迹管理；利益相关者理论；信息不对称理论；产品全生命周期管理；绿色供应链管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
